replies.text: I was kind of hoping they would have like a second attack on the same scale as the Capitol to end the season and move the plot forward sa season 2. But I guess they shot the season finale before knowing if they were going to be renewed and just decided to magically catch everybody (except that one guy) in the last 10 minutes and have Kirkman give a speech so that the series ends well if no renewal
sabi namin ni jet while watching, sabog ulet para designated survivor ulet, tapos si state sec/old prez yung may pakana ng lahat... but no... just a super korny speech.
